sheet.description:
Decks of cards count as improvised weapons for you; they have the thrown (30/60) and finesse properties and deal 1d4 + {{dexterity:modifier}} damage on hit. Once per turn you can roll a d4 to grant a playing card attack an additional effect:
(1) Reduce the target's movement speed by {{pick a card speed}} ft.;
(2) This attack counts as a Sneak Attack;
(3) Gain the damage dealt as temporary hit points;
(4) You can switch initiative order with the target starting next round
